---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Translation Pricing Guide Dubai | OnlineTranslation.ae"
  description="Understanding legal translation pricing in Dubai. Factors that affect costs, typical price ranges, and how to get an accurate quote."
>
  <section class="hero-section bg-dark" data-theme="dark">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">HOME</a>
        <span class="separator">&gt;</span>
        <a href="/resources/">RESOURCES</a>
        <span class="separator">&gt;</span>
        <span class="current">PRICING GUIDE</span>
      </nav>
      
      <h1>Translation Pricing Guide</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Understanding Costs</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">Translation pricing varies based on several factors. This guide helps you understand what affects costs and what to expect when requesting a quote.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container content-container">
      <h2>Factors That Affect Pricing</h2>
      
      <div class="factor-grid">
        <div class="factor-card">
          <div class="factor-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i></div>
          <h3>Document Type</h3>
          <p>Standard certificates (birth, marriage, degrees) are typically priced per page. Complex legal documents (contracts, court filings) may be priced per word or at a project rate due to specialized terminology.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="factor-card">
          <div class="factor-icon"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div>
          <h3>Document Length</h3>
          <p>Longer documents generally cost more but may qualify for volume discounts. Multi-page documents from the same project are often discounted compared to individual submissions.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="factor-card">
          <div class="factor-icon"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></div>
          <h3>Turnaround Time</h3>
          <p>Standard turnaround is typically same-day to 3 working days. Express and urgent services are available at premium rates for time-sensitive requirements.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="factor-card">
          <div class="factor-icon"><i class="fas fa-language"></i></div>
          <h3>Language Pair</h3>
          <p>Arabic-English translations are our specialty and priced competitively. Other language pairs may have different pricing based on translator availability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container content-container">
      <h2>What Is Included</h2>
      
      <div class="included-list">
        <div class="included-item">
          <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
          <span>MOJ certification and official stamp</span>
        </div>
        <div class="included-item">
          <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
          <span>Digital copy (PDF) via WhatsApp or email</span>
        </div>
        <div class="included-item">
          <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
          <span>Certified hard copy with original stamp</span>
        </div>
        <div class="included-item">
          <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
          <span>Same-day delivery within Dubai (orders before 2 PM)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="included-item">
          <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
          <span>Quality review and accuracy check</span>
        </div>
        <div class="included-item">
          <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
          <span>7-day error correction guarantee</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h3>Additional Services (Optional)</h3>
      
      <div class="additional-list">
        <div class="additional-item">
          <span class="service-name">MOFA Attestation</span>
          <span class="service-desc">Ministry of Foreign Affairs authentication</span>
        </div>
        <div class="additional-item">
          <span class="service-name">Embassy Legalization</span>
          <span class="service-desc">Country-specific embassy authentication</span>
        </div>
        <div class="additional-item">
          <span class="service-name">Notarization</span>
          <span class="service-desc">Notary public attestation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="additional-item">
          <span class="service-name">Courier Pickup</span>
          <span class="service-desc">Collection of original documents from your location</span>
        </div>
        <div class="additional-item">
          <span class="service-name">Express Delivery</span>
          <span class="service-desc">Delivery to other Emirates</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container cta-section">
      <h2>Get an Accurate Quote</h2>
      <p>The easiest way to get a precise quote is to send us your document. We will review it and provide a detailed price within minutes.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/971508620217" class="btn btn-primary">
        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Send Document for Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-section { padding: 8rem 0 4rem; background: var(--primary-color); }
  .breadcrumb { font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .breadcrumb a { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: #ffffff; }
  .breadcrumb .separator { margin: 0 0.5rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); }
  .breadcrumb .current { color: #ffffff; }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #ffffff; }
  .hero-subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--accent-color); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero-intro { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 700px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); }
  .content-container { max-width: 800px; }
  .factor-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .factor-card { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; }
  .factor-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--primary-color); color: #ffffff; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .factor-card h3 { margin: 0 0 0.75rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .factor-card p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .included-list { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .included-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; padding: 1rem; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .included-item i { color: var(--accent-color); font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .additional-list { background: #ffffff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; }
  .additional-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  .additional-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .service-name { font-weight: 600; }
  .service-desc { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .cta-section { text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cta-section h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-section p { margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--accent-color); color: #ffffff; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #e0144c; transform: translateY(-2px); }
</style>
